full_text: @ReitzelTodd When you are watching a live game and it goes past its time on the guide, what you have to do is go back to the schedule and then select the show that is labeled as "on now", this will get you back to the transmission of the game. -JG
full_text(utf-8): b'@ReitzelTodd When you are watching a live game and it goes past its time on the guide, what you have to do is go back to the schedule and then select the show that is labeled as "on now", this will get you back to the transmission of the game. -JG'

Select Add Channel 
Relaunch your newly installed Sling TV app. LK

full_text:
@BearsCubs77 Press the Home button on your remote
Choose Settings in the top right
Select All Settings in the bottom right
Choose General on the left
Scroll down and select About this TV
Make sure Allow automatic updates is checked, then select Check for updates. LK

b'@BearsCubs77 Press the Home button on your remote

Select All Settings in the bottom right
Choose General on the left
Scroll down and select About this TV
Make sure Allow automatic updates is checked, then select Check for updates. LK'
